`,(0,t.jsxs)(e.p,{children:["In following the default ",(0,t.jsx)(e.a,{href:"https://open-next.js.org/inner_workings/architecture",children:"OpenNext architecture"})," recommendations, the various AWS services this site uses\u2014primarily Lambda, S3, CloudFront\u2014means the cost of it all is quite tiny. AWS has fairly generous free tier limits, and I\u2019ll likely stay fairly well within them for this particular application (a portfolio/blog). This is helped enormously by serving the site via CloudFront\u2019s CDN."]}),`
